      <title>特朗普案件仍未结案，选举法律纠纷迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/election-legal-fights-loom-with-trump-cases-still-stuck-in-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 试图推翻 2020 年大选结果，但旷日持久的法庭争斗仍未解开谜团，即美国司法系统将如何应对 11 月总统大选后出现的类似动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/election-legal-fights-loom-with-trump-cases-still-stuck-in-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 15:06:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
